PRIVILEGE ESCALATION QUICK REFERENCE
LINUX:
sudo -l (what can I run as root?)
find / -perm -4000 2>/dev/null (SUID binaries)
cat /etc/crontab (cron jobs)
id (what groups am I in?)
uname -a (kernel version - check for kernel exploits)
WINDOWS:
whoami /priv (check privileges)
whoami /groups (check groups)
systeminfo (OS version - check for exploits)
net user (list users)
net localgroup administrators (who is admin?)
